notes: Upper bound assumes withdrawn stake is rewards-first: sum(min(rewards_claimed, withdraw_amount))
Proxy assumes principal inflow = bond_additional + stake_claimed; attributes withdraw beyond that to rewards (capped by rewards)
These are on-chain bounds/proxies for stake leaving BondingManager; they do not prove off-chain selling (DEX/CEX)
Does not account for TransferBond stake transfers (can shift where withdrawals occur)
